description: Brighten up your party decor with American Football Paper Lanterns. Our faux lanterns are football-shaped globes with sturdy wire frames, printed to look like real footballs, complete with laces. They arrive flat but pop open for a three-dimensional display, indoors or outdoors. Perfect as party decorations and man-cave additions. Decorating for your Super Bowl Party or team banquet will be quick and easy with these decorations. Each lantern measures about 13.5 inches in length. Go long!
